Tools that help startups monitor their web services:

- [New Relic](http://newrelic.com/) - monitors the health and performance of web services
- [Pingdom](https://www.pingdom.com/) - sends notifications of web service downtime
- [PagerDuty](http://www.pagerduty.com/) - sends SMS notifications of web service downtime/errors
- [Exceptional](http://www.exceptional.io/) - error/exception tracking
- [Unbounce](http://unbounce.com/) - Landing Page host, with A/B split testing and other features, use code lean3100 to get first three months free
